    "url": "https://bppimt.ac.in/admission/other-under-graduate-courses/",
    "content": "Under Graduate Courses (BBA, BCA) - B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Skip to content 98364 36999 B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Approved by AICTE, New Delhi & Affiliated to MAKAUT, W.B Home › Admission › Under Graduate Courses (BBA, BCA) Under Graduate Courses (BBA, BCA) Share on Facebook Share on X (Twitter) Share on Whatsapp Share on Telegram Share on Email BBA , BBA (Business Analytics) & BCA- 3years In addition to our main campus offerings, B. P. Poddar Institute of Management and Technology also operates a dedicated Salt Lake Campus , focused on professional undergraduate programs in business and IT. Students can choose from: Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA) Bachelor of Business Administration in Business Analytics (BBA-BA) Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA) All programs are affiliated to Maulana Abul Kalam Azad University of Technology (MAKAUT), approved by AICTE/UGC, and designed to build strong foundations for careers in business, analytics, and IT. Eligibility For BBA, BBA (Business Analytics) and BCA UG Courses Passed / appeared / due-to- appear in 2025 at the Higher Secondary Examination in the General or Vocational Stream under the West Bengal Council of Higher Secondary Education or its equivalent examination / Undergraduate Program as prescribed from a recognized Board / University. Successful candidates once admitted in affiliated college or in the University, will have to undergo special prerequisite audit bridge Program, as decided by the University, if required. Common Entrance Test (CET) Rank Card For New Admission in BBA, BBA (Business Analytics) & BCA Stream Valid Rank Card through CET Examination (conducted by MAKAUT, WB) is mandatory for all Students. About Common Entrance Test (CET) The Maulana Abul Kalam Azad University of Technology, West Bengal (MAKAUT, WB) and its affiliated institutions jointly administer the conduct of CET. The CET Board as constituted by the Maulana Abul Kalam Azad University of Technology, West Bengal, is the sole authority to conduct the examination and declare the results. CET is an all India examination for admission in Under Graduate and Post Graduate professional Program offered in-house by Maulana Abul Kalam Azad University of Technology, West Bengal and by its affiliated colleges. No Provision for admission under any Reserved Category Quota viz SC,ST, OBC, Minority and PwD candidate. Uniform is mandatory (Available from Institute recommended Dressmaker) Apply for Common Entrance Test BPPIMT Salt Lake Campus B.P.Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Salt Lake Campus, EN-31 Salt Lake Sector V, Kolkata – 700091, West Bengal, India 91 33 2357-2509 +91 80 17 65 2567 +91 76 04 06 9622 [email protected] bppimt.com Contact our city office for admission related queries B.P.Poddar Institute of Management and Technology 87, Park Street (Opp St. Xavier’s College, Beside Park Street Police Station) Kolkata – 700016 91-033-2265 7150 91-033-2265 7152 +91 98364 36999 [email protected] Mr. Santanu Banerjee Related Pages Admission Post Graduate Course (M.Tech) Post Graduate Course (MCA) Under Graduate Courses (B.Tech) Under Graduate Courses (BBA, BCA) Scholarship Schemes Quick Links Affiliating University NIRF NBA Mandatory Disclosure Archive New sletters Events Achievements Media Coverage Human Resources Board of Governors Administration Academic Advisory Body Technical Staff Forum & Cell Internal Quality Assurance Cell Internal Complaint Committee Important Cells Important Links Institute Login Salt Lake Campus Greivance Redresal Misc. Information B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Approved by AICTE, New Delhi & Affiliated to MAKAUT, W.B 137, V.I.P Road, Poddar Vihar, Kolkata - 700052 91-033-40619174 / 75 / 76 [email protected] Privacy Policy © 2026 B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Designed & Developed by INSPIRE STUDIO Search for:",
