    "title": "Computer Facility",
    "url": "https://bppimt.ac.in/central-facilities/computer-facility/",
    "content": "Computer Facility - B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Skip to content 98364 36999 B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Approved by AICTE, New Delhi & Affiliated to MAKAUT, W.B Home › Central Facilities › Computer Facility Computer Facility Share on Facebook Share on X (Twitter) Share on Whatsapp Share on Telegram Share on Email Computer Centre The Institute has two Computer Centers consist of computers with latest configuration connected through Campus LAN (wired and Wi-Fi) to provide support to the students and staffs for computing and browsing. Computer Laboratory Other than Computer Centre Institute has 11 computer Laboratories to facilitate the Laboratory classes. Special Wi-Fi zone has been created to cater for the LAN facility so as to enable them to have a concrete hands-on experience and be abreast with the latest Software Technologies. The Computer Centre facilitates the smooth running of Laboratory Classes in the respective specialized laboratories predetermined for the purpose. Programming Laboratory Data-Structure Laboratory Artificial Intelligence Laboratory Operating System and System Programming Laboratory Network Programming Laboratory Database Management System Laboratory Simulation Laboratory Java, Object Technology and Web Technology Laboratory Computer Organization and Architecture Laboratory Project Laboratory Internet Facility The entire campus is interconnected through a high-speed fiber optic backbone, ensuring reliable and efficient communication across all buildings. The institute is equipped with a dedicated 450 Mbps (1:1) leased internet line , providing uninterrupted 24×7 connectivity. This robust network infrastructure enables seamless intra-campus and remote access, supporting academic, research, and administrative activities with high performance and reliability. GPU Computing Facility The institute offers a state-of-the-art high-performance GPU computing facility accessible to students and staff anytime, anywhere. With secure 24×7 access available both on-campus and remotely, users can leverage powerful computational resources using credentials provided by the Computer Center — enabling advanced research, AI/ML development, and high-end data processing seamlessly. System Support Mr. Anagh Pramanik (Network Administration and Support) Mr. Bhabani Sankar Adak (System Maintenance) Mr. Bijoy Das (Network Administration and Support) Mr. Atanu Paul (IT Help Desk) Mr. Kailash Das (IT Help Desk and Support) Related Pages Central Facilities Language Laboratory Computer Facility Sports and Games Facilities Quick Links Affiliating University NIRF NBA Mandatory Disclosure Archive New sletters Events Achievements Media Coverage Human Resources Board of Governors Administration Academic Advisory Body Technical Staff Forum & Cell Internal Quality Assurance Cell Internal Complaint Committee Important Cells Important Links Institute Login Salt Lake Campus Greivance Redresal Misc. Information B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Approved by AICTE, New Delhi & Affiliated to MAKAUT, W.B 137, V.I.P Road, Poddar Vihar, Kolkata - 700052 91-033-40619174 / 75 / 76 [email protected] Privacy Policy © 2026 B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Designed & Developed by INSPIRE STUDIO Search for:",
