    "content": "Language Laboratory - B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Skip to content 98364 36999 B. P. Poddar Institute of Management & Technology Approved by AICTE, New Delhi & Affiliated to MAKAUT, W.B Home › Central Facilities › Language Laboratory Language Laboratory Share on Facebook Share on X (Twitter) Share on Whatsapp Share on Telegram Share on Email The first of its kind, the Language Laboratory, installed by CACM, STEP, IIT Kharagpur links multi- user Interactive Software Integrated Learning System (ISILS). This makes content delivery and interactive set up development with digitized contents on language and communication skill development smoother. The ever expanding bank of books, CDs, DVDs, and more which deal with English Speech and Communication contribute in personality development Instructor microphone to all users; Headset/PA Systems Computer Audio for all users; Headset/PA Systems One-on-one Talk Sessions AUX or other source to all users; Headset/PA Systems Complete open house situation with recording facility Activities of Language Laboratory through Centre for Advanced Communication (CACM) Interactive Software Integrated Learning System (ISIL) Activities at a Glance Interactive sessions between students and faculty for enhancing the audio verbal skills Pronunciation practice Audio-visual clippings for developing interpretation and speaking skills Audio-visual demonstrations on presentation skills including body language and practice Group discussions Ice breaking techniques Developing reading aloud and comprehension skills Enhancing public speaking skills Mock interviews Personality development Related Pages Central Facilities Language Laboratory Computer Facility Sports and Games Facilities Quick Links Affiliating University NIRF NBA Mandatory Disclosure Archive New sletters Events Achievements Media Coverage Human Resources Board of Governors Administration Academic Advisory Body Technical Staff Forum & Cell Internal Qualit